    • Method Detail

      • add

        void add(IChartObject chartObject)
        Adds the object of type IChartObject to the current panel. The object is locked by default. Note that only one object instance can be added per chart.
        Parameters:
        chartObject - - instance of IChartObject super type.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - - if object is already present on chart.

      • remove
